<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Allium dumebuchum A habit B inflorescence C underground structure (r = rhizome) D tepal and filament arrangement E Flower F pistil G capsule H seed. Photos by H. J. Choi: H. J. Choi 201008 - 001 (A, B, D-F) and H. J. Choi 070001 (C, G, H)." , "Figure 1. Comparative photographs of the inflorescence, cross-section of leaf and scape, flower, and tepal and filament arrangement of Allium section Rhizirdeum in South Korea and northeastern China A-E A. dumebuchum (H. J. Choi 201008 - 001) F-J A. spirale (H. J. Choi 191010 - 01) K-O A. spurium (H. J. Choi 200831 - 01) P-T A. minus (H. J. Choi 080063) U-Y A. senescens (H. J. Choi 080119)." , "Figure 3. Mitotic metaphase chromosomes and their voucher plants of Allium species A A. dumebuchum (H. J. Choi 190917 - 01) B A. spirale (H. J. Choi 191010 - 01) C A. spirale (H. J. Choi 190910) D A. spurium (H. J. Choi 080390) E A. spurium (H. J. Choi s. n.) F A. senescens (H. J. Choi 080119, voucher plant: Fig. 2 of Choi and Oh 2010)." , "Figure 6. Phylogenetic tree of Allium section Rhizirideum and related taxa based on concatenated alignments of four cpDNA regions (ndhJ - trnF, trnH - psbA, psbD - trnT, and psbJ - petA). The numbers above branches are bootstrap values (BS> 50 %) by maximum likelihood method. The samples of section Allium Rhizirideum and the new species are in blue and red blods, respectively. The accession numbers from Genbank were indicated after the scientific names." , "Figure 5. Distribution map of Allium dumebuchum and its related species section Allium dumebuchum Rhizirideum in Korea and northeastern China (revised from Sinitsyna et al. 2016)." , "Figure 2. Principal components analysis plot of five Allium species of section Allium Rhizirideum in South Korea and northeastern China. dum = A. dumebuchum; min = A. minus; sen = A. senescens; spi = A. spirale; spu = A. spurium." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531585" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531582" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531586" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531583" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531587" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531584" .

